{"tid":1047432,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"15 16 俄妹定美女","createTime":"2019-03-05T02:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T07:09:17.000Z","uid":136539,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d49f9f3cc2b41837183e6695740492a6f3686a41","tid":1047432,"uid":136539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"之前放錯台 無人理我😢<br />\n<br />\nplan 緊同男友去grad trip<br />\n心大心細<br />\n俄羅斯 定 關島好？<br />\n🇷🇺<br />\n俄羅斯應該睇建築 食環境多<br />\n去啲名勝 聖巴索大教堂 紅場<br />\n🇬🇺<br />\n關島就算係香港人最中意海外結婚 度蜜月既地方<br />\n玩sky dive 出海睇海豚 陽光海灘 玩射箭 揸飛機<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會玩skydive 揸飛機<br />\n關島物價好似貴d<br />\n但我地唔識俄文 驚好難溝通 <br />\n<br />\n究竟會唔會去俄羅斯淨係睇睇睇好悶？<br />\n但去關島唔玩佢最出名既活動又好似唔抵？<br />\n<br />\np.s. 另外會同一班fd grad trip去泰國<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打絲打去過 比下意見呀？"},{"pid":"d6ba2e61516cadb1aaaf082422af334d7f7e8130","tid":1047432,"uid":37661,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"去屌閪就去長洲得啦。"},{"pid":"c4b1464adf524d28b32ca189d1c418611c5c2b40","tid":1047432,"uid":56452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6ba2e61516cadb1aaaf082422af334d7f7e8130","tid":1047432,"uid":37661,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"去屌閪就去長洲得啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a7adc44aa120575c913237394400e77a68ffe5","tid":1047432,"uid":45459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ba2e61516cadb1aaaf082422af334d7f7e8130","tid":1047432,"uid":37661,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"去屌閪就去長洲得啦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"呢句真"},{"pid":"e12260d1ce36775a61f48415aba1e5ed990c4e1f","tid":1047432,"uid":201604,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 <br />\n仲以為有15 16歲既美女俄妹睇"},{"pid":"a04114eb7adebb166a08c35c2fc25e4d0a8cdc49","tid":1047432